                    "body": "Hello Neal, thanks for the info. Problems with the Apache mirrors sound like a reasonable explanation. But I had consistent build failures over several hours, and again on the following morning. So it was probably more than just a single bad mirror.\r\n\r\nAfter the binary failure yesterday, I did another build with source download. The installation succeeded, but unit tests failed, so there is still a problem in my environment. I'm trying again now. I'll close this issue, because the source downloads seem to be working again.",
